data.description: BACK TO ACTIVE.  BUYER COULD NOT PERFORM-FINANCING!  TOUR TODAY AND MAKE YOUR OFFER!   Meticulously kept and super clean townhome in Creekside Village!   Great opportunity to own a spacious, sun-lit, bright, airy, 3-bedroom, 3 full bath home!   This beauty has a bonus bedroom/office on the entry level.  A “good to be home” feeling with a sense of community and family is what you will find here.  This open-floor plan property offers 9-foot ceilings, pristine hardwood floors, carpeted flooring, full size separate living room and dining room, central A/C, ON DEMAND hot water heater, granite counter tops, deep brown kitchen cabinets, large kitchen island, stainless steel appliances, entry level bedroom, spacious finished basement, recessed lighting, upper-level laundry facility with large capacity front load washer and dryer, and primary bedroom luxury shower.  Enjoy entertaining on the maintenance-free composite deck.     Fall in love with the community amenities - including pools, basketball and tennis courts, tot-lot, fitness center, dog parks, and walking trails, (low HOA fee). Set the stage for a show-stopping Anne Arundel County lifestyle! The superb market location brims steps away from shopping, dining, and doing!  Curious about what makes Anne Arundel County so wonderful? Live like a local and find out for yourself.   Amazingly priced.  Property being sold AS-IS.  Convenient to 695, 295, and 95.   NO ASSIGNMENTS! NO WHOLESALERS!  Schedule your tour today!
